<section>
	<title>IPv6</title>
	<section>
		<title>禁用 IPv6</title>
		<para>有些 Linux 发行版会将 ipv6 设为默认，国内 ipv6 支持不好，导致网络出现异常</para>
		<para>创建文件 /etc/sysctl.d/ipv6.conf</para>
		<screen>
		<![CDATA[
net.ipv6.conf.all.disable_ipv6 = 1
net.ipv6.conf.default.disable_ipv6 = 1
net.ipv6.conf.lo.disable_ipv6 = 1
net.ipv6.conf.eth0.disable_ipv6 = 1
		]]>
		</screen>
		
	</section>
	
	
</section>